@startuml
title Hình 4.14 - Biểu đồ tuần tự luồng tìm kiếm sản phẩm theo CQRS-lite

skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultTextAlignment center
skinparam roundcorner 8
skinparam ArrowColor #475569
skinparam ArrowThickness 1.3
skinparam ParticipantBorderColor #475569
skinparam ParticipantBackgroundColor #F1F5F9
skinparam DatabaseBorderColor #475569
skinparam DatabaseBackgroundColor #DCFCE7
skinparam QueueBorderColor #475569
skinparam QueueBackgroundColor #FEF3C7

actor "Admin" as Admin
actor "Customer" as Customer
participant "API Gateway" as Gateway
participant "product-service\nCommand side" as Product #DCFCE7
database "product_db\nPostgreSQL" as ProductDb
queue "Kafka" as Kafka
participant "search-service\nQuery side" as Search #DBEAFE
database "Elasticsearch\nproducts index" as Es

== Command path: cập nhật sản phẩm ==
Admin -> Gateway : POST/PUT /api/products
Gateway -> Product : authenticated admin request
Product -> ProductDb : insert/update product
Product -> Kafka : publish product-created\nor product-updated
Product --> Gateway : product saved
Gateway --> Admin : response

Kafka -> Search : consume product event
Search -> Es : upsert product document\nname, description, category,\nbrand, price

== Query path: tìm kiếm sản phẩm ==
Customer -> Gateway : GET /api/search?q=...
Gateway -> Search : route to search-service
Search -> Es : full-text query\nfilters/sort/pagination
Es --> Search : ranked product documents
Search --> Gateway : search results
Gateway --> Customer : products

note bottom
  PostgreSQL là write model do product-service sở hữu.
  Elasticsearch là read model tối ưu tìm kiếm.
  Đồng bộ qua Kafka, chấp nhận eventual consistency ngắn.
end note

@enduml
